quran[9{c,v,t}:
27,14,aur be insafi aur ghuroor se un se inkaarkiya lekin un ke dil un ko maan chuke they. so dekh lau fasaad karne walon ka injaam kaisa howa
27,15,aur hum ne dawod aur Sulaiman ko ilm bakhsha aur unhon ne kaha ke khuda ka shukar hai jis ne hamein bohat se momin bundon par fazliat di
27,16,aur Sulaiman aur dawod ke qaim maqam hue. aur kehnay lagey ke logo! hamein ( khuda ki taraf se ) janwaron ki boli sikhayi gayi hai aur har cheez inayat farmai gayi hai. be shak yeh ( uss ka ) Sarih fazl hai
27,17,aur Sulaiman ke liye junoo aur insanon aur parindon ke lashkar jama kiye gay aur qisam waar kiye jatay they
27,18,yahan taq ke jab chyontyon ke maidan mein puhanche to aik choonti ne kaha ke chyontyon apne apne bilon mein daakhil ho jao aisa nah ho ke Sulaiman aur is ke lashkar tum ko kuchal dalain aur un ko khabar bhi nah ho
27,19,to woh is ki baat sun kar hans parre aur kehnay lagey ke ae perwar-digaar! mujhe tofeq ataa farma ke jo ahsaan tunay mujh par aur mere maa baap par kiye hain un ka shukar karoon aur aisay naik kaam karoon ke to un se khush hojaye aur mujhe apni rehmat se apne naik bundon mein daakhil farma
27,20,unhon ne janwaron ka jaiza liya to kehnay lageykiya sabab hai ke hudhud nazar nahi aata.kiya kahin gayab hogaya hai ?
27,21,mein usay sakht saza dun ga ya zibah kar daloon ga ya mere samnay ( apni be Qasuri ki ) Daleel Sarih paish kere
27,22,abhi thori hi der hui thi ke hudhud aa mojood howa aur kehnay laga ke mujhe aik aisi cheez maloom hui hai jis ki aap ko khabar nahi aur mein aap ke paas ( shehar ) Saba se aik sachhi khabar le kar aaya hon
